quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  40,17,"Nyanga yino buli Omundu alarungwa kayakholanga. Olwa lelo okhukholilwa obubii khubulaho. Toto Nyasaye ni Omwangu wokhubala (ebikhole)."
  40,18,"Ne bekanyilisie inyanga ili ahambi, olwa emioyo chiliula khwiporokotio nabo nibayinjilwe neshibeela, abamabii shibaliba nende Omwitsa nohomba ubasabila yawulilwa tawe."
  40,19,"Yamanya okhukatia khwetsimoni nende ka ebilifu bifisanga."
  40,20,"Ne Nyasaye abusinjia khubwatoto, ne balia babalaamanga abalali Nyasaye tawe shibabusinjia shiosishiosi tawe. Toto Nyasaye ni Omuwulili muno, Omuloli muno."
  40,21,"Shibachendangakhwo khushialo mana balola indukho yabalia bali imbeli wabu yali irie tawe? Bali nende amaani amaanji okhubashila, nende ebikhole ebikhongo khushialo, mana Nyasaye nabatila obutinyu khutsimbi tsiabu, mana shibalikho nende wokhubakhonya okhurulana nende eshinyasio shia Nyasaye tawe?"
  40,22,"Endio nilwokhuba mbu Abarumwa babu babetselanga nende ebifune bia habulafu mana nibakhaya, ne Nyasaye nabatila. Toto ye niwa amaani, weshinyasio eshilulu."
  40,23,"Ne toto khwaruma Musa halala nende ebimanyisio biefu nende ebifune bia habulafu."
  40,24,"Khu Firauni, nende Hamana nende Qarun, mana nibaboola mbu: “Uno ni omulosi omubeyi muno.”"
  40,25,"Olwa yabeetsela nende obwatoto okhurula khwifwe, baboola mbu: “Yire abana abasiani ba balia basuubila ninaye, mana muleshe abana babu abakhana.” Ne ebifwanga bia abakhayi shibili wosiwosi tawe halali mubukori."